verbose_text: Fractions from Tg (flk1 :d sRed; cmyb : GFP) embryos (1,000 embryos / sample x 3 replicate sorts) sorted with fluorescence activated cell sorting (FACS) showed vdra expression in endothelial niche cells (Flk1 :d sRed + / cMyb : GFP -) and HSPCs (Flk1 :d sRed + / cMyb : GFP +) (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY).
